CustomField.description: The reviews are to determine the number of transactions processed by Australia Post for each of the Services in the twelve (12) month period preceding the review date. Based on the review, if the Principal falls into a different Volume Level bracket, the Transaction Fees payable by the Principal will be adjusted from the applicable review date.
